data.description: This is a very well maintained and updated family home.  Great curb appeal with a nice landscaped yard, concrete drive and side entry garage.  There is lots of family living space downstairs with the remodeled kitchen open to the family room, a breakfast nook, formal dining, a sunroom and a large office which could be used as a flex space if you don't need a home office.  There are four bedrooms - the smallest one opens to the hallway and also to the master bedroom - makes it a great nursery space if needed or a large dressing area, reading space, home gym or craft room.  wood floors downstairs and on the stairway while the upstairs bedroom space is carpeted.  Large yard partially fenced. Two storage buildings - one is wired and built out for a workshop.
